cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the software (Zenodo) and the dataset (HydroShare) below."
title: "Non-stationary groundwater pumping behavior and coupled groundwater forecast uncertainty"
abstract: >-
  Code to reproduce the analyses and figures in Hu & Xi, "From pumping regime
  shifts to groundwater forecast uncertainty in coupled human-groundwater
  models". Pipeline: deep temporal clustering, Bayesian
  changepoint detection, stationary vs. regime-aware XGBoost pumping models,
  bootstrap ensembles, and propagation through the RRCA MODFLOW-2000 model.
